{"tid":2069893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（中學生、大專生入）學生歷量招募成員！","createTime":"2020-06-18T17:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T05:04:05.000Z","uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"185e089b948b8cebffaac290369014e745122968","tid":2069893,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"【學生歷量成員招募】<br />\n對象：中五、中六或大專學生<br />\n條件：<br />\n具備充分責任感 及<br />\n擁有捍衛香港的決心 及<br />\n支持及認同全民制憲 及<br />\n願意付出汗水和時間<br />\n<br />\n申請表格: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/dhzXjQfCLfEo1FHs6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FdhzXjQfCLfEo1FHs6&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=32a845c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/dhzXjQfCLfEo1FHs6</a> <br />\n<br />\n如有任何疑問，歡迎Instagram direct至 @hkgstudentspower 或電郵至 hongkongstudentspower@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n［組織簡介］<br />\n學生歷量是一個本土學生組織。自反修例運動掀起，香港陷於水深火熱之處，兩位大專生共同創立組織，誓要為社會略盡綿力，以星星之火與大眾共同對抗暴政。<br />\n<br />\n本組織於2019年8月15日正式成立。致力投入社會運動，引發香港學生的政治關注及參與。同時參與地區工作，將本土意識帶入社區。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n［組織宗旨］<br />\n「殊途同歸 」&mdash; 話解雖則經行不同路線方法，但終究也會抵達於同樣的目的地。<br />\n<br />\n我們略以「殊途同歸」一語代表自己的宗旨。縱使學生歷量的觀點與泛眾的看法理念也許是大相逕庭、不盡相同，但歸根究底，大家始末也同樣以捍護普世共同價值與保衞香港獨特文化為目標。就如「殊途同歸」之意，途程甚殊但歸處盡同。 <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n學生歷量 Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgstudentspower\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgstudentspower&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=3cb4c3d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgstudentspower</a><br />\n<br />\n學生歷量 Instagram<br />\n<a href=\"http://instragram.com/hkgstudentspower\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstragram.com%2Fhkgstudentspower&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=182ee74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instragram.com/hkgstudentspower</a><br />\n<br />\n學生歷量 Telegram<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkgstudentspower\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkgstudentspower&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=42a05d28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkgstudentspower</a><br />\n<br />\n#成員招募 #本土 #本土學生組織 #香港人 #全民制憲 #殊途同歸 #學生歷量"},{"pid":"a68d4019259186ad3470c6b4fdb7b648405358a4","tid":2069893,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1255f6984498bc49c3e9f0345e781e127dae44a","tid":2069893,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T18:56:39.000Z","msg":"how much?"},{"pid":"8a9bbe1cb3d0032bdcafbf1fc41f0f4656b72196","tid":2069893,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T23:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8ee031252f642067a9d66879e70341cb444ada","tid":2069893,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T05:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}